snippet.title: Game Dev Tycoon | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Design blockbuster games, build your studio from the ground up and become part of video game history in this super-satisfying business simulation.

Play Game Dev Tycoon NETFLIX on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81636737

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
